event_name: Sweat and Cider at Fraser Valley Cider Company
description: Join Nadi at the Fraser Valley Cider Company for a perfect summer night — an evening of dance and cider! Grab your besties and join us for a 1- hour Zumba class followed by a refreshing glass of your favorite cider to cool down and celebrate. This class is all about good vibes only — think upbeat music, easy-to-follow moves, and a beautiful outdoor space to let go, dance and just feel the joy. Whether you’re brand new or a Zumba regular, you’re welcome here. Remember to bring water and dress for the weather! Doors Open: 6:00pm Class time: 6:30pm - 7:30pm Stay after for a complimentary glass of cider, beer, wine or non-alcoholic option from our mobile bar. Thinking Dinner? Our full food menu will also be available. Please note - this session will be taking place outdoors on uneven ground. This is an all ages event!
